Package: cf-nginx
Version: 1.0.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: nginx, curl, jq, systemd
Recommends: certbot, python3-certbot-nginx
Maintainer: CF-NGINX Team <contact@example.com>
Description: Cloudflare IP manager for NGINX
 Automatically fetches and updates Cloudflare IP ranges in NGINX
 configurations with daily auto-updates and SSL integration.
 .
 One command to enable: cf-nginx enable <site>
 - Detects if SSL is present
 - Offers to install SSL if missing  
 - Adds CF IPs to all server blocks
 - Tests config before applying
 - Auto-rollback on failure
 .
 Commands: cf-nginx, cf-nginx-manual, cf-nginx-validate
